Class TodayEpisode

java.lang.Object
  TodayEpisode

public class TodayEpisode
extends java.lang.Object

This Object holds all Infos about a show in the Countdown XML

  • Show ID
  • Show name
  • Show link
  • Episode link
  • Episode title
  • Season and episode number
  • Air date
  • Relative date
